attributes.Long form description: The student is assembling a black table. They start by attaching the legs, then the top. They use screws, tightening some with an Allen wrench.

attributes.Transcription: Now we're going to build this furniture so please assemble this furniture.

attributes.Action sentence: The student inspects the black table and its legs.

attributes.Transcription: You should set up by taking one of the shells, the long side down on the table. The longer side of the table

attributes.Incorrect Action Explanation: The student should not drop the leg.

attributes.Transcription: Try to attach one of the legs. This shelf is going to be the middle shelf so you should put the legs that this shelf, becomes the middle shelf.

attributes.Action sentence: The student assembles the middle leg and the table.
The student inserts the first screw into one of the table's legs.
The student tries to insert the second screw into the leg of the table.

attributes.Incorrect Action Explanation: The student should not drop the hex_socket_head.

attributes.Action sentence: The student inserts the second screw into the leg of the table.

attributes.Transcription: You should rotate the shelf and the leg on the table to put the other way. So that the leg is standing on the on the table.

attributes.Action sentence: The student inserts the third screw into the leg of the table.
The student tries to insert the fourth screw into the leg of the table.
The student inserts the fourth screw into the leg of the table.
The student inserts the fifth screw into the leg of the table.
The student inserts the sixth screw into the leg of the table.
The student inserts the seventh screw into the leg of the table.
The student inserts the eighth screw into the leg of the table.
The student rotates a black table and screws the legs.

attributes.Action Correctness: Wrong Action, corrected by instructor verbally
attributes.Incorrect Action Explanation: The student should not rotate the furniture.

attributes.Transcription: You should have the furniture still laying on the side to *unintelligible*.

attributes.Action sentence: The student assembles the top table and its leg.
The student inserts a screw into the first leg of the table.
The student inserts a screw into the second leg of the table.
The student inserts the thirteenth screw into the leg of the table.
The student tries to insert the fourteenth screw into the leg of the table.

attributes.Incorrect Action Explanation: The student should not drop the hex_socket_head.

attributes.Action sentence: The student inserts the fourteenth screw into the leg of the table.

attributes.Transcription: Please make sure that every screw is well screwed by more than you can.

attributes.Action sentence: The student tightens the top screws with an Allen wrench.
The student tightens the middle screws with an Allen wrench.

attributes.Transcription: It's over. You can press this button.
